snippet.title: Animals are so funny that you can die of laughter - Funny animal compilation
snippet.description:
Here is the best, funniest, cutest and most ridiculous animal / pet video clips collection. From funny cat fails, to monkeys, penguins, goats, ridiculous dogs and so on. I bet you can't watch it till the end without laughing :P Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!

WANT TO SEE YOUR PET IN OUR COMPILATIONS?
Send your clips or links to: tigerlicensing@gmail.com

For more funny videos & pictures visit and like our Facebook page:
https://www.facebook.com/tigerstudiosfun
